  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how the mobile application for booking household waste
    collection services (the “App”) processes users’ personal data. The App is developed
    and operated by ЭКО-ГН (sole proprietor Mammadov Kanan Jalal) (“we”, “us”, “our”).
  </p>

  <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
  <p>We collect and process only the data that is necessary to book and provide waste collection services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email address (for registration and communication);</li>
    <li>Phone number (for communication and order confirmations);</li>
    <li>Home or service address (pickup location for waste collection);</li>
    <li>Name of the service recipient (which may differ from the account owner);</li>
    <li>Telegram contact or other specified messenger account (for quick communication);</li>
    <li>Order history (dates, times, addresses and status of collections).</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    We do not collect or store credit card numbers or other payment credentials.
    Payments are processed by a third-party payment provider (for example, YooMoney),
    which has its own privacy policy.
  </p>

  <h2>2. How we use the data</h2>
  <p>We use personal data strictly for the following purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Registering and managing the user account;</li>
    <li>Creating, modifying and fulfilling waste collection orders;</li>
    <li>Contacting the user and the service recipient by phone, e-mail or messenger;</li>
    <li>Ensuring security and preventing fraud (for example, checking suspicious orders);</li>
    <li>Improving the quality of our service and resolving technical issues.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Sharing of data with third parties</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>
  <p>Access to certain data may be provided to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Couriers and service personnel who perform the waste collection – only to the
      extent necessary (address, order time, recipient’s name, contact details);
    </li>
    <li>
      The payment provider (for example, YooMoney) – only to the extent required to
      process the payment; your card details remain with the payment provider and are
      not shared with us;
    </li>
    <li>
      Government authorities – only where required by applicable law or a valid legal request.
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Data storage and security</h2>
  <p>
    Data is stored on our server resources and used solely for operating the App and
    providing our services. We take technical and organisational measures to protect
    data against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure or destruction.
  </p>
  <p>
    Data is retained for as long as your account is active or as necessary to provide
    the services and comply with legal obligations. After your account is deleted,
    personal data is deleted or anonymised, except where we are required by law to
    retain certain information (for example, for accounting or tax purposes).
  </p>

  <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>request information about the personal data we hold about you;</li>
    <li>request correction of inaccurate data;</li>
    <li>request deletion of your account and associated data, where permitted by law;</li>
    <li>withdraw your consent to data processing (in which case use of the App may become impossible).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Account and data deletion</h2>
  <p>
    You can request deletion of your account and related data by following the
    instructions on this page:
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="https://rasah673.github.io/Eko-QN-Privacy-policy/delete-account.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      https://rasah673.github.io/Eko-QN-Privacy-policy/delete-account.html
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>
    After receiving your request, we will delete your personal data (email, phone,
    addresses, recipient name, order history), except for data that we are legally
    required to keep for a certain period.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Children</h2>
  <p>
    The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 18. We do not knowingly
    collect data from children. If you believe that a child’s data has been provided to us
    without the consent of a legal guardian, please contact us so that we can delete it.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Changes to this Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The current version will always
    be available on this page. Your continued use of the App after any changes are made
    means that you accept the updated Policy.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
  </p>
  <p><strong>kenan7304@mail.ru</strong></p>
  <p><strong>Moscow, Yuzhnobutovskaya Street, Building 51, Apartment 18</strong></p>
